---
import BaseLayout from "../../../components/BaseLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../../../components/Hero.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="支持 / Support - BillLoopr" description="BillLoopr support page in Chinese and English.">
  <Hero
    compact
    kicker="BillLoopr"
    title="支持 / Support"
    zh="用于 BillLoopr App 支持、隐私问题和数据删除指引。"
    en="For BillLoopr app support, privacy questions, and data deletion guidance."
  />
  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="bilingual">
        <article class="contact-card">
          <span class="lang-label">中文</span>
          <h3>联系支持</h3>
          <p>支持邮箱：<a href="mailto:2578033436@qq.com">2578033436@qq.com</a></p>
          <p>请尽量附上 App 版本、设备型号、系统版本和简要问题描述。通常会在 3-5 个工作日内回复。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="contact-card">
          <span class="lang-label">English</span>
          <h3>Contact support</h3>
          <p>Support email: <a href="mailto:2578033436@qq.com">2578033436@qq.com</a></p>
          <p>Please include your app version, device model, system version, and a short description of the issue when possible. We usually respond within 3-5 business days.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="bilingual">
        <article class="prose-card">
          <span class="lang-label">中文</span>
          <h3>常见帮助主题</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>记录可计费工时前，可以先创建客户和项目。</li>
            <li>使用计时器记录工作时段，并在开票前检查记录。</li>
            <li>使用发票记录来准备、预览、分享和管理计费文档。</li>
            <li>通过 App 内删除入口移除客户、项目、发票、时间记录或相关数据。</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="prose-card">
          <span class="lang-label">English</span>
          <h3>Common help topics</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Create clients and projects before recording billable time.</li>
            <li>Use the timer to record work sessions and review the result before invoicing.</li>
            <li>Use invoice records to prepare, preview, share, and manage billing documents.</li>
            <li>Use in-app delete controls to remove clients, projects, invoices, time entries, or related records when available.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
      <article class="prose-card content-stack">
        <section class="callout">
          <h3>数据与隐私 / Data and privacy</h3>
          <div class="bilingual">
            <p>BillLoopr 无需注册 BillLoopr 账号即可使用。App 记录保存在设备本地；iCloud 可用时，也可能通过你的 Apple 账号私密同步到其它设备。导出和分享仅由你主动触发。</p>
            <p>BillLoopr works without creating a BillLoopr account. App records are stored locally and, when iCloud is available, may sync privately across devices through your Apple Account. Exports and sharing happen only when you choose them.</p>
          </div>
          <p><a href="/billloopr/privacy/">隐私政策 / Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </section>
        <section class="callout">
          <h3>非财务建议 / Not financial advice</h3>
          <div class="bilingual">
            <p>BillLoopr 帮助整理时间、项目、收入和发票记录，不提供税务、法律、会计、银行或支付处理服务。</p>
            <p>BillLoopr helps organize time, project, income, and invoice records. It does not provide tax, legal, accounting, banking, or payment processing services.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
